For An Act To Be Entitled
9
10 AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE IVERMECTIN FOR HUMAN USE TO BE
11 SOLD WITHOUT A PRESCRIPTION OR CONSULTATION WITH A
12 HEALTHCARE PROFESSIONAL; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
13
14
Subtitle
15
16 TO AUTHORIZE IVERMECTIN FOR HUMAN USE TO
17 BE SOLD WITHOUT A PRESCRIPTION OR
18 CONSULTATION WITH A HEALTHCARE
19 PROFESSIONAL.
20
21 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
22
23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 20, Chapter 7, Subchapter 1, is amended
24 to add an additional section to read as follows:
25 20-7-147. Ivermectin without prescription or consultation with
26 healthcare professional.
27 (a) As used in this section, "over-the-counter medication" means
28 medication that may be legally sold and purchased without a prescription.
29 (b) Notwithstanding any law to the contrary, ivermectin suitable for
30 human use may be sold or purchased as an over-the-counter medication in this
31 state without a prescription or consultation with a healthcare professional.
